Class Model<ChildModelRecord> 

java.lang.Object
  framework.Model<ChildModelRecord>
Direct Known Subclasses:
FieldModel, ImageModel, ProjectModel, RecordModel, UserModel 
public abstract class Model<ChildModelRecord>
				
extends java.lang.Object

An abstract Model template from which all the custom models inherit.

It is used like : public class CustomModel extends Model { }

This allows us to perform the generic SQL statement queries that are shared between all the models like find() or findBy() or findAll() etc. Ideally, we would define RELATIONSHIPS in the custom models and leave as much of the SQL requests to the generic model.
